 {"id":"bd-4cb8f","title":"add mounted-path ext4 CASEFOLD lookup and readdir coverage","description":"Survey finding: ext4 CASEFOLD parity is currently frozen in conformance-only OpenFs tests, while README/FEATURE_PARITY describe case-insensitive lookup as an operator-visible behavior. Scope: add a mounted-path ext4 FUSE test image with a casefold-enabled directory and prove case-insensitive lookup plus readdir visibility through the mounted path, including a representative sharp-s or mixed-case lookup. Acceptance: fuse_e2e freezes operator-visible CASEFOLD lookup/readdir behavior instead of only the in-process conformance path.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"ubuntu","created_at":"2026-04-21T08:44:05.519756375Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-22T05:26:00Z","closed_at":"2026-04-22T05:26:00Z","close_reason":"Stale in-progress sweep: no commit reference after more than 12 hours; closed per operator instruction so the work can be re-filed or reclaimed cleanly.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
